title: XTCS Counter-Strike 1.6 Final Release 2014
description:
About the Game
Just want to say and warn many, it is only the renewal of our old version, do not expect any global changes.

What's new in this version:
- Version of the game has been updated to the latest version of the protocol 48 (build 4554)
- Work Internet bookmarks and Favorites
- Some minor bug fixes 

Features:

* Fully working serverbrowser with MasterServer
* Latest release of the game, V43, Build 4554.
* Dual Protocol (48 + 47) Client
* Added option to launch listen server in LAN mode
* Included Bots in this release
* Half-Life maps are totally removed
* HLTV included and works
* Ads are removed
* Antislowhack tool included
* Download and Play

Release: 01/04/2014
